tr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hjb1665702800243.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hjb1665702800243.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hjb1665702800243.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hjb1665702800243\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                 \n Define DTD Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define optional DTD properties.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__p_d5810e1_d5811e1_d5812e1\">The DTD properties defined on this form are not required by Uniface, but can be required by 3GL components.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__section_kyb_yx2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d724187e56\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__ul_bd5_yx2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__li_d2927e1_d2928e1_d2929e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jtp1665702800385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtp1665702800385.html\" title=\"Suffix of the entity name, which represents a namespace. The model name can be used to group entities and DTDs that are logically related in some way.\">Model Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__li_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hlv1665702654431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hlv1665702654431.html\" title=\"Unique name for the DTD.\">DTD Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__li_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hlv1665702654431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hlv1665702654431.html\" title=\"Unique name for the DTD.\">DTD Name</a>\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mxp1665702654645.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mxp1665702654645.html\" title=\"Name of the text file to which the Uniface DTD is compiled.\">File Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__li_d2936e1_d2937e1_d2938e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pxy1665702654725.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pxy1665702654725.html\" title=\"Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) for the Uniface DTD. This can be used by non-Uniface components to locate the DTD. Uniface can include this URI in XML streams based on the current DTD.\">External Reference</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__li_d2939e1_d2940e1_d2941e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tnh1665702654577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tnh1665702654577.html\" title=\"Default mapping between element names in the DTD and Uniface field and entity names. This property contains an associative list ( GOLD ; separated) list of DTD element-Uniface name pairs.\">Default Mapping</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__section_cpz_yx2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d724187e120\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hjb1665702800243__p_d5819e1_d5820e1_d5821e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qkw1665702654897.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkw1665702654897.html\">Working with DTDs</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420257\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420257\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define DTD Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define DTD Properties Define optional DTD properties. The DTD properties defined on this form are not required by Uniface, but can be required by 3GL components. Fields Model Name DTD Name DTD Name File Name External Reference Default Mapping How to Working with DTDs Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}